'''INFJ'''（内倾/直觉/情感/判断）是[[迈尔斯·布里格斯性格分类法|迈尔斯·布里格斯性格分类法]]中十六种人格类型之一，在柯尔塞气质类型测试中被称为'''[[咨询师_(角色变异)|咨询师]]'''，属于[[理想者_(气质类型)|理想者]]的四种类型之一。<ref name=foundation>{{cite web|url=http://www.myersbriggs.org/my-mbti-personality-type/mbti-basics/the-16-mbti-types.asp|title=Myers-Briggs Foundation: The 16 MBTI Types|accessdate=2011-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090513191631/http://www.myersbriggs.org/my-mbti-personality-type/mbti-basics/the-16-mbti-types.asp|archive-date=2009-05-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

INFJ是最稀少的类型之一，大概佔人口的1%，其中男性INFJ最為罕見，僅佔0.25%。<ref name=Counselor/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.infj.org/archive/typestats.html|title=MBTI Statistics '98|accessdate=2011-02-03|archive-date=2008-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724234931/http://www.infj.org/archive/typestats.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Estimated Frequencies of Types | url = http://www.capt.org/mbti-assessment/estimated-frequencies.htm | publisher = Center for Applications of Psychological Type, Inc. | accessdate = 2011-02-03 | archive-date = 2017-09-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170911215111/https://www.capt.org/mbti-assessment/estimated-frequencies.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>當代著名的INFJ名人有[[哈利波特|哈利波特]]的作者[[J·K·羅琳|J·K·羅琳]]。<ref name="#1">{{cite news|url=https://mobile.twitter.com/jk_rowling/status/806543288790634498|title=J.K. Rowling: I'm INFJ|3=|accessdate=2019-05-11|archive-date=2019-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017114723/https://mobile.twitter.com/jk_rowling/status/806543288790634498|dead-url=no}}</ref>

